Deep Convolutional Auto-Encoders model -v1.1
Change list: 1. Discard some subjects with 0 value of features in dataset ABIDE II, FCP 2. Split data pre-processing into 3 parts and store in 3 files: DCAE_data.hdf5, DCAE_folds.hdf5 and DCAE_scheme.hdf5 3. Preprocessing data as follows: (1) Per-example mean subtraction and unit variance (2) Feature Standardization of pre_train_data and train data in each fold, then save the mean and std used for feature standardization of valid data and test data.

Deep Convolutional Auto-Encoders model -v1.2
Change list: 1. Add scheme 5: multi-view convolutional neural network with spatial pyramid pooling. 2. ROIs are selected by independent two-sample t-test of functional connectivity.
